I knew from the beginning

00:00:17.601 --> 00:00:19.603
That we would get along well

00:00:27.653 --> 00:00:28.403
No, I...

00:01:02.604 --> 00:01:04.231
Since when have you been here?

00:01:05.607 --> 00:01:07.943
Me? For about an hour?

00:01:10.237 --> 00:01:12.906
But what kind of dream did you have

00:01:12.906 --> 00:01:14.241
That made you break out in a cold sweat?

00:01:14.574 --> 00:01:17.160
No, it's okay

00:01:18.870 --> 00:01:21.289
Jaemin, did something happen?

00:01:21.873 --> 00:01:23.250
Your face is pale

00:01:24.418 --> 00:01:25.711
